chickenGPT: Ferdinand the frog 🐸 croaked, "Chirp! Medicine time, 10 PM!" Henrietta the chick 🐥 usually chirped back, "Thanks, Ferd!" But tonight? Silence. Henrietta was dreaming of worms 🪱. Ferdinand, exasperated, hopped into the henhouse, flicked a tiny pebble at her head. Henrietta woke with a squawk! 💥 "Oh! Medicine! Sorry, Ferd! You're a lifesaver, or a life-croaker!" She gulped it down. Ferdinand just rolled his eyes. 🙄
